commit.message: Merge branch 'feature/new-backend' of https://github.com/revanthgss/social-core into revanthgss-feature/new-backend
Merge branch 'send-proxies-in-request' of https://github.com/bajibabu9/social-core into bajibabu9-send-proxies-in-request
Add changelog entry for zoom backend

Improve error handling of id_token decoding in AppleIdAuth backend.

The try: block should include these additional lines, as PyJWTError can
be raised there too if id_token is malformed.

Fix exception raising in the AppleIdAuth backend.

1. AuthFailed is more appropriate than AuthCanceled for these
   situations.
2. AuthXXX(self, error_message) is the correct usage, not
   AuthXXX(error_message).

Use callable builtin instead of ABC

Co-Authored-By: Serhiy Storchaka <storchaka@gmail.com>
Fix warnings regarding invalid escape sequences and base64.
Merge branch 'partial-cleanup-bug' of https://github.com/jaywhy13/social-core into jaywhy13-partial-cleanup-bug
